l-what-fire-brings/">Rachel Howzell Hall on Grief, Strength, and the Purifying Nature of Fire</a></strong><span class="post_attribute center"><span class="post_detail_date">June 20, 2024</span> by <a href="https://crimereads.com/author/nancieclare/">Nancie Clare</a></span></div></li><li><div class="post_circle_thumb"><a href="https://crimereads.com/matthew-hart-diamonds-essay/"><img class="lazy" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/plugins/lb-content-widgets/img/lazy-sq.png" data-src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2024/06/diamond1-150x150.jpg" alt=""></a></div><div class="text-container"><strong class="title"><a href="https://crimereads.com/matthew-hart-diamonds-essay/">How Lab-Grown Diamonds Upended the Industry and Could End Up Changing the World</a></strong><span class="post_attribute center"><span class="post_detail_date">June 20, 2024</span> by <a href="https://crimereads.com/author/matthewhart/">Matthew Hart</a></span></div></li><li><div class="post_circle_thumb"><a href="https://crimereads.com/red-hot-and-blue-a-defense-of-agatha-christies-the-mystery-of-the-blue-train/"><img class="lazy" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/plugins/lb-content-widgets/img/lazy-sq.png" data-src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2024/06/mystery-of-the-blue-train-feat-150x150.jpg" alt=""></a></div><div class="text-container"><strong class="title"><a href="https://crimereads.com/red-hot-and-blue-a-defense-of-agatha-christies-the-mystery-of-the-blue-train/">Red, Hot and Blue: A Defense of Agatha Christie’s <em>The Mystery of the Blue Train</em></a></strong><span class="post_attribute center"><span class="post_detail_date">June 18, 2024</span> by <a href="https://crimereads.com/author/curtisevans/">Curtis Evans</a></span></div></li></ul></li>
